OL,3,CMeghan tells Australian students she
OL,4,Cwas 'most trolled person' in the world
OL,6,FSpeaking in a classroom on the third
OL,7,Fday of her Australian visit, Meghan
OL,8,Fsaid social media companies were "not
OL,9,Fincentivised to stop".
OL,11,F"And I can speak to that really
OL,12,Fpersonally, which is why I like to
OL,13,Flisten, because it rings true for me
OL,14,Fin a very real way," she said.
OL,16,F"For now, 10 years, every day for 10
OL,17,Fyears, I have been bullied and
OL,18,Fattacked. And I was the most trolled
OL,19,Fperson in the entire world."
OL,26,@pD@bOUqD@UO]sD@AOUvD@TO]xD@AOU{D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
