OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776352251
OL,3,CMeghan tells Australian students she
OL,4,Cwas 'most trolled person' in the world
OL,6,FBatyr was founded in 2011 by Sebastian
OL,7,FRobertson, who decided to share his
OL,8,Fexperience of mental ill-health to
OL,9,F"normalise conversations and provide
OL,10,Fhope to young people going through
OL,11,Ftough times".
OL,13,FThe organisation, named after an
OL,14,Felephant in a Kazakhstan zoo which was
OL,15,Fclaimed to be able to use more than 20
OL,16,Fhuman phrases, works to address a
OL,17,F"youth mental health crisis in
OL,18,FAustralia".
OL,26,@qD@AOUsD@LO]yD@AOUzD@JO]
